=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n愈靚料愈貴，始終啲靚嘅原材料本身個價都唔係平</blockquote><br />\n邊隻好用？<br />\n我用neutrogena</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://4goskincare.blogspot.hk/2016/06/resist-super-light-wrinkle-defense-spf.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F4goskincare.blogspot.hk%2F2016%2F06%2Fresist-super-light-wrinkle-defense-spf.html%3Fm%3D1&d=X1LzviS17SySsPZJwcPYb4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=fa4f7f61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://4goskincare.blogspot.hk/2016/06/resist-super-light-wrinkle-defense-spf.html?m=1</a><br />\n呢隻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf421596e21f0b2218b14ab32e951d31c8257352","tid":266291,"uid":42867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:21:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>回應返正題:.試下高登暗瘡神藥skinoren，藥房買~</blockquote><br />\n少少印都啱用？</blockquote><br />\n個人認為冇乜用 搽左三個月仲係一pat屎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34905407196024fda88e1f10ec683275f0ee761a","tid":266291,"uid":45238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇一啲防曬介紹 ，唔好咁敏感嗰啲</blockquote><br />\n你日常用，定強烈戶外活動用？<br />\n要化學防曬定物理防曬？<br />\nBudget 幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n底過500<br />\n<br />\n日常<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁傷皮膚就好了，因為我塊面好敏感</blockquote><br />\n你有無研究過對咩敏感，定係純粹整體都好易敏感？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇呀， 但係我係好容易就生pimples, 之前用過Watson's 啲護膚嘢，最後攪到成塊面紅晒，又la</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Watson 都敢用。100%伏黎<br />\n基本上，查上臉一定買日本製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本野一般真係比較有保証<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都要記得睇成份</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以依家我乜都無用到<br />\n<br />\n其實係唔敢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05c8d4a5ad79db24a1ca2a366f6e712e84b3460","tid":266291,"uid":6715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做海藻矽針</blockquote><br />\n咩黎 要打針？</blockquote><br />\n好似磨沙咁 facial其中一種 係做完會有摻刺嘅感覺"},{"pid":"0d54699aafc510ef08781798d2577f492de55536","tid":266291,"uid":656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做海藻矽針</blockquote><br />\n咩黎 要打針？</blockquote><br />\n好似磨沙咁 facial其中一種 係做完會有摻刺嘅感覺</blockquote><br />\n呢隻係用極高濃度嘅酸逼你煥膚，係好有效但好刺激<br />\n慎用"},{"pid":"acb8156f83f74681deb397a90f60ee4036241aad","tid":266291,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做海藻矽針</blockquote><br />\n咩黎 要打針？</blockquote><br />\n好似磨沙咁 facial其中一種 係做完會有摻刺嘅感覺</blockquote><br />\n呢隻係用極高濃度嘅酸逼你煥膚，係好有效但好刺激<br />\n慎用</blockquote><br />\n同激光比邊個好d"},{"pid":"d2db59ea605058c5e0d91cf3bb0f1bcf77a1cc0e","tid":266291,"uid":656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做海藻矽針</blockquote><br />\n咩黎 要打針？</blockquote><br />\n好似磨沙咁 facial其中一種 係做完會有摻刺嘅感覺</blockquote><br />\n呢隻係用極高濃度嘅酸逼你煥膚，係好有效但好刺激<br />\n慎用</blockquote><br />\n同激光比邊個好d</blockquote><br />\n唔同性質，矽針係處理印，激光係窿<br />\n比較唔到"},{"pid":"4a5d25b0b07c15d3af62ac2d0d49ce6c1e7f7335","tid":266291,"uid":92636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T13:56:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做海藻矽針</blockquote><br />\n咩黎 要打針？</blockquote><br />\n好似磨沙咁 facial其中一種 係做完會有摻刺嘅感覺</blockquote><br />\n呢隻係用極高濃度嘅酸逼你煥膚，係好有效但好刺激<br />\n慎用</blockquote><br />\n同激光比邊個好d</blockquote><br />\n唔同性質，矽針係處理印，激光係窿<br />\n比較唔到</blockquote><br />\n我有做開矽針，去印好有效<br />\n但真係好刺激 好痛好紅<br />\n但一定要搵信得過嘅美容院<br />\n上網見好多人買料自己做 係平 但你整得唔好會出事<br />\n一定要等冇曬瘡先做<br />\n做完最好留喺屋企兩三日等佢甩皮<br />\n多啲做保濕gel mask<br />\n另外有隻產品叫spot peel都係用酸換膚"},{"pid":"fa33d9a56561238cec23e6efa27e4c44bdd195ca","tid":266291,"uid":92636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T13:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做海藻矽針</blockquote><br />\n咩黎 要打針？</blockquote><br />\n好似磨沙咁 facial其中一種 係做完會有摻刺嘅感覺</blockquote><br />\n呢隻係用極高濃度嘅酸逼你煥膚，係好有效但好刺激<br />\n慎用</blockquote><br />\n同激光比邊個好d</blockquote><br />\n唔同性質，矽針係處理印，激光係窿<br />\n比較唔到</blockquote><br />\n我有做開矽針，去印好有效<br />\n但真係好刺激 好痛好紅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以￼</span>一定要搵信得過嘅美容院<br />\n上網見好多人買料自己做 係平 但你整得唔好會出事<br />\n一定要等冇曬瘡先做<br />\n做完最好留喺屋企兩三日等佢甩皮<br />\n多啲做保濕gel mask<br />\n另外有隻產品叫spot peel都係用酸換膚</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8c560d12f4a8e787fa06101de5288c0786adf7fb","tid":266291,"uid":28201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:38:00.000Z","msg":"借post一問，有冇人知呢幾粒係咪暗瘡？<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/04/163648_ac20a4521959cebc9eca7da542459ad3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F163648_ac20a4521959cebc9eca7da542459ad3.jpg&h=8fc131ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n生係心口個位到，最大個粒又冇濃頭喎，最大個粒仲要生咗好耐，分分鐘生咗有兩年，愈嚟愈大粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到而家個size開始冇再大"},{"pid":"fa0db600ee0320037829caf0a8b51f38080e0f26","tid":266291,"uid":92636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:19:31.000Z","msg":"生咗兩年唔係暗瘡喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cae891425a47e809dc2a5101373f17d964dc478","tid":266291,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生咗兩年唔係暗瘡喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nKeep住有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cl